# Netlify/Bolt redirects — evaluated top-to-bottom; first match wins.
# Static HTML rewrites MUST appear before the SPA catch-all so crawlers get
# full pre-rendered content (Gmail landings, Smash Leads, pSEO pages).

# Blog posts (with and without trailing slash)
/blog/:slug           /blog/:slug/index.html   200
/blog/:slug/          /blog/:slug/index.html   200

# Gmail × accounting SEO landing pages
/integrations/gmail-quickbooks-estimate-generator    /integrations/gmail-quickbooks-estimate-generator/index.html    200
/integrations/gmail-xero-quote-builder               /integrations/gmail-xero-quote-builder/index.html               200
/gmail-invoice                                       /gmail-invoice/index.html                                       200
/xero                                                /xero/index.html                                                  200
/xero/                                               /xero/index.html                                                  200
# /b2b-gmail-quoting is a full React route (parity with /chrome-extension) — no static shadow.

# Smash Leads CRM hub (before /:country/alternatives patterns)
